parameters: I scouted ahead. We're halfway there, but there
I saw the one with the shield \C[14]protecting the
others.\C[0] Maybe you can try to \C[5]crush his shield.
The mace guy's got \C[10]powerful, stunning blows,\C[0] so be
careful. Try to get at him with a \C[14]knife or a spear.
The one in the back \C[10]throws nets\C[0] - he's definitely
the most dangerous. Maybe you can \C[14]pierce and
shoot him \C[0]through his nets. Take him out first.
